maeher
=========

This package wraps the REAPER (Robust Epoch And Pitch EstimatoR) library
originally written by David Talkin at Google, Inc.

REAPER upstream source
----------------------
Copyright 2015 Google Inc. All rights reserved.
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
Original source: https://github.com/google/REAPER

The C++ source files under cpp/reaper/ are reproduced from that repository
with no algorithmic modifications.  The only change is the removal of two
diagnostic fprintf(stdout, ...) calls in epoch_tracker.cc (ComputeFeatures),
made so the library is thread-safe (no concurrent writes to the process-wide
stdout) and does not clutter the console on every call.  Numerical output is
unaffected.

